00:48:43,316 --> 00:48:44,984
All right, then, you're good to go.

1208
00:48:45,068 --> 00:48:48,946
In five, four, three, two…

1209
00:48:49,030 --> 00:48:50,698
Welcome back. Our next guest

1210
00:48:50,782 --> 00:48:52,992
is no stranger to you. Or to plates.

1211
00:48:53,076 --> 00:48:54,368
It's the comedienne Sophie Lennon,

1212
00:48:54,452 --> 00:48:56,078
but don't turn that dial…

1213
00:48:56,162 --> 00:48:58,289
-That's nice.
-…because this is going to be

1214
00:48:58,373 --> 00:48:59,999
a fascinating conversation.

1215
00:49:00,083 --> 00:49:01,792
I'm gonna make sure.
Come on out here, Sophie.

1216
00:49:01,876 --> 00:49:03,961
-♪♪
-[APPLAUSE]

1217
00:49:10,259 --> 00:49:11,678
[MOUTHS]

1218
00:49:18,685 --> 00:49:21,395
So… Sophie Lennon.

1219
00:49:21,479 --> 00:49:24,398
Just how nutsy whacko are you?

1220
